(84, 4, 1, 'Coding bootcamps address tech industry talent shortage', '<h2>üíª Coding Bootcamps: Fast-Track to Tech Careers</h2><p><strong>Intensive coding bootcamps</strong> have emerged as an <em>effective solution</em> to bridge the gap between <u>tech industry hiring needs</u> and available talent.</p><h3>Bootcamp Model:</h3><h4>Program Features:</h4><ul><li>üöÄ <strong>Duration:</strong> 12-24 weeks intensive training</li><li><strong>Focus Areas:</strong> Software development, data science, cybersecurity</li><li><strong>Hands-on Learning:</strong> 80% practical projects</li><li><strong>Industry Curriculum:</strong> Skills employers actually need</li><li><strong>Career Support:</strong> Job placement assistance</li></ul><h4>Popular Tracks:</h4><p>Bootcamps offer <em>specialized career paths</em>:</p><ol><li><strong>Full-Stack Development:</strong> MERN/MEAN stack</li><li><strong>Data Science:</strong> Python, ML, analytics</li><li><strong>Cybersecurity:</strong> Ethical hacking, network security</li><li><strong>Mobile Development:</strong> iOS/Android apps</li><li><strong>Cloud Computing:</strong> AWS, Azure certifications</li></ol><h3>Success Metrics:</h3><h4>Graduate Outcomes:</h4><ul><li>üíº <strong>Placement Rate:</strong> 85-90% employed within 3 months</li><li><strong>Starting Salaries:</strong> ‚Çπ6-12 lakhs per annum</li><li><strong>Career Switchers:</strong> 60% from non-tech backgrounds</li><li><strong>Employer Satisfaction:</strong> 92% would hire bootcamp grads again</li></ul><h4>Industry Partnership:</h4><p><strong>Educational institutions</strong> are embracing the model:</p><ul><li><strong>University Collaborations:</strong> Hybrid degrees + bootcamp</li><li><strong>Corporate Tie-ups:</strong> Hiring partner networks</li><li><strong>Apprenticeships:</strong> Earn while you learn programs</li><li><strong>Scholarships:</strong> Financial aid for deserving candidates</li></ul><blockquote>\"Coding bootcamps democratize access to tech careers. They offer an accelerated, practical learning path that traditional education sometimes lacks. For career switchers and recent graduates, bootcamps provide the specific skills and portfolio projects needed to land that first tech job,\" said bootcamp founders.</blockquote><p>Your <strong>tech career</strong> starts here! üë®‚Äçüíª</p>', 'article-4-1619459128.webp', '2021-06-15', 1, 1),
(85, 5, 2, 'Green bonds attract institutional investors', '<h2>üå± Green Finance Revolution: Bonds Oversubscribed Within Hours</h2><p>The government\'s issuance of <strong>green bonds</strong> to finance <em>renewable energy and sustainable infrastructure</em> projects has received <u>overwhelming response</u> from institutional investors.</p><h3>Bond Details:</h3><h4>Issue Specifications:</h4><ul><li>üí∞ <strong>Issue Size:</strong> ‚Çπ10,000 crores</li><li><strong>Tenor:</strong> 10-year maturity</li><li><strong>Interest Rate:</strong> Competitive 7.25% coupon</li><li><strong>Purpose:</strong> Renewable energy and green infrastructure</li></ul><h4>Subscription Success:</h4><p>The bonds were <em>massively oversubscribed</em>:</p><ol><li><strong>Within Hours:</strong> Fully subscribed in 3 hours</li><li><strong>Oversubscription:</strong> 3.5 times the issue size</li><li><strong>Investor Types:</strong> Insurance, pension funds, banks</li><li><strong>Foreign Investors:</strong> 30% subscribed by FIIs</li></ol><h3>Use of Funds:</h3><h4>Project Allocation:</h4><ul><li>üåç <strong>Solar Power:</strong> ‚Çπ4,000 crores for solar farms</li><li><strong>Wind Energy:</strong> ‚Çπ2,500 crores for wind projects</li><li><strong>Green Transport:</strong> ‚Çπ2,000 crores for electric mobility</li><li><strong>Energy Efficiency:</strong> ‚Çπ1,500 crores for building retrofits</li></ul><h4>Environmental Impact:</h4><p>Expected <strong>positive outcomes</strong> from funded projects:</p><ul><li><strong>Carbon Reduction:</strong> 5 million tons CO2 annually</li><li><strong>Renewable Capacity:</strong> 3,000 MW additional</li><li><strong>Green Jobs:</strong> 50,000+ employment</li><li><strong>Air Quality:</strong> Reduced pollution in cities</li></ul><blockquote>\"This overwhelming response reflects growing investor interest in environmentally responsible investment opportunities. Green bonds allow investors to earn returns while supporting climate action and sustainable development